We serve the Agencies that serve the Public!
Welcome to our Web site, where you'll find a wealth of information in the form of newsletter articles, calculators, and research reports.
 
 
 
 
 
Public Agency Financial Consultants (PAFC) was formed by Andy Fass and Steve Stahlberg, to assist Public Agencies and Institutions by offering investment advice for Reserve/Surplus funds, Retirement Plans and Other Post- Employment Benefits (OPEB) programs. We offer advice that is appropriate, in line with applicable statutes and codes, understandable, transparent and meets the goals and objectives of our clients. PAFC understands the importance of meeting the parameters of those State Codes that relate to Safety of Principal, Liquidity and Return.
We go to great lengths to ensure that all investment decisions and portfolio compositions fall within the parameters of those guiding regulations and principals, and match our clients' fiduciary obligations and responsibilities.
Hilltop Securities Overview
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 











